## PRODUCT VISUALIZATION
Visualize **invisible** trust beautifully: atmospheric signal rendering, trust flow, identity pulse choreography, intelligent verification paths — **alive, calm, mathematically precise**. Avoid generic network graphics and security clipart.

## MOBILE
Mobile is **primary**: native-feeling, cinematic, tactile, luxurious; outdoor readability; OLED-friendly; touch comfort; finger occlusion aware.

## INTERACTION
Buttons feel **engineered**; hovers **emotionally soft**; touch **physical**; micro-interactions communicate trust, precision, predictability — nothing accidental.

## ICONOGRAPHY
**Proprietary** geometric system: timeless, civic, intelligent, engineered, globally institutional — not generic icon libraries.

## DEPTH & ATMOSPHERE
Environmental gradients; translucent trust surfaces; floating depth; ambient light diffusion — **atmospheric**, not mechanically layered.

## ACCESSIBILITY
World-class **without** visual compromise: contrast targets, dynamic scaling, motion sensitivity, screen readers, keyboard nav — accessibility feels **native**, not bolted on.

## LOADING
Never blank: atmospheric loading, trust-pulse transitions, elegant skeletons, environmental fades.

## DEVELOPER SURFACES (docs / portals)
Rival Stripe · Vercel · Linear · OpenAI: beautiful API presentation, code blocks with perfect syntax hierarchy, mathematical spacing, restrained dark transitions, SDK elegance.

## DESIGN SYSTEM ENGINEERING
Systematic **spacing, radius, timing, opacity, motion, typography scale, icons, responsive framework, component architecture** — nothing arbitrary.

## TECHNICAL STACK (where applicable)
Next.js, Tailwind, Framer Motion; premium rendering; cinematic animation architecture; reusable components; responsive-first; accessibility-first; smooth performance; modular composition.

